    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter in regards to the article that you have printed in your newspaper The Times of India on 8th December, 19 about the upcoming movie of Kiara Adwani. I would like to tell you that she is a very close friend of mine, and I know her personally since we were in school.",
        "In this article, you have mentioned that her upcoming movie is \u201cKabir Singh 2\u201d. I would like to tell you that her upcoming movie is \u201cGood News\u201d which is releasing next month. Though, the date of release of \u2018Kabir Singh 2\u2019 is not yet decided.",
